narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: It will teach you a lot about Japanese culture. Yes. Very interesting readings and movies.
Enjoyable continuation of earlier L5 curriculum. Good for building and maintaining reading and writing skills.
I would definitely recommend this course to anybody who wants to approach/achieve fluency in Japanese.
Seto-sensei makes the class very enjoyable and the material is great. Be prepared to put in work to get the most out of this class. It's great for keeping up your Japanese.

Seto sensei is a great instructor, and although the extreme workload can be frustrating at times, this class is the best way for advanced learners of Japanese to continue their progress in the language.
